	functions.

	* lily/note-collision.cc (do_shifts): align colliding notes to
	their leftmost note.

	* input/regression/collision-alignment.ly: new file.

	* ly/init.ly: don't print gc stats.

	* scripts/lilypond-book.py (Lilypond_snippet.output_texinfo): add
	extra newline

